{"tid":1658122,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［Be Water 極致］鄰舍家庭裝修計劃","createTime":"2019-10-16T11:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T13:46:38.000Z","uid":21678,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c0584ed9d407916540165145361ffb99ce0b169e","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"唔鼓吹暴力，純學術討論<br />\n<br />\n抗爭者街頭裝修+裝飾<br />\n主要目標，就係切斷紅色資金對巿場控制<br />\n一步一步咁阻止佢地對政權輸血<br />\n同時阻嚇鄉黑勢力抬頭蔓延<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果有人將呢套裝修理念<br />\n套用響一啲「社會英雄」身上，咁又會點呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n有冇可能削弱佢哋，甚至響各個家庭中製造內在矛盾呢？"},{"pid":"379133b696abda803629cd60dce961acf7b3542d","tid":1658122,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0qWEWOF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0qWEWOF.jpg&h=c3e7c9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vvxT1fm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvvxT1fm.jpg&h=5485129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/52d75G2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F52d75G2.jpg&h=c42abc3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d2f222a0fa1ae5072fe1d0fd7706c329f9dc77c","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:50:45.000Z","msg":"有興趣幫人做義務工作嘅您<br />\n首先<br />\n就係要搵夠三五知己<br />\n自己一個人太危險，一有工傷就麻煩<br />\n<br />\n第二<br />\n就係由最接近自己屋企嘅地方出發<br />\n最好近到連笠都唔駛搭<br />\n<br />\n第三<br />\n時間任擇<br />\n子夜、清晨、傍晚<br />\n只要有心，幾時都可以係裝修日<br />\n<br />\n施恩莫望報，有啲嘢唔駛咁張揚<br />\n裝修完記得帶好隨身物品<br />\n拎番屋企先好掉呀"},{"pid":"f0e6714cbf49dc95cea5214f056e4f8e2184c43a","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:52:12.000Z","msg":"重有最重要一點<br />\n鄰舍裝修，最緊要係保持安靜<br />\n因為好多人好醒瞓<br />\n嘈親其他隔離鄰取就唔好啦"},{"pid":"947dab741e033ebc1f7b1a07ca02f3f70f65e6ea","tid":1658122,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"Target係邊個？"},{"pid":"fa160ec35d54d4bd0bedbc8503671b28e6e218a3","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"簡單如換過把鎖呢啲舉手之勞<br />\n唔會好張揚<br />\n不過對方一定好感激你"},{"pid":"6fec753d585fdb96c7d5e0a7a402537cea3aa87a","tid":1658122,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:56:24.000Z","msg":"支持軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90b52cc3b421669ed36e2c9193c769bace5a4d6","tid":1658122,"uid":60635,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:57:47.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0afe25d2fccaf6fab5770d0c4131ae6848b8b245","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"947dab741e033ebc1f7b1a07ca02f3f70f65e6ea","tid":1658122,"uid":149534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:53:21.000Z","msg":"Target係邊個？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:59:18.000Z","msg":"Blockchain 好似有好多好鄰舍資料<br />\n需要大家支持"},{"pid":"2b858f163d4d6045b903f8643338950d5c8933b9","tid":1658122,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:00:05.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB搵我地香港自由之書阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係呀,我知我地講近廢話,但前線的確需要支援</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1655137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書"},{"pid":"d0e14d15519d1b420f5290501646dd5d8a4ffd3d","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:07:19.000Z","msg":"作為一個裝修佬<br />\n為保安全，記住任何時間，都需要全套保護衣<br />\n唔好似為冇人睇到就偷懶<br />\n你點知幾時有CCTV影住你唔跟安全標準開工<br />\n手套眼罩呢啲一定唔少得"},{"pid":"fcc1472addc2601403d72509fb0eda3a955c9eab","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3b2f67435b6d0c79c890ea48e29fb390e8896e6","tid":1658122,"uid":83543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T12:44:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5225e5a60815cf1c36a95f7ff132ecd6170a11c8","tid":1658122,"uid":21678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:46:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecf4d26dccbdff6938dd114f69b355c453d2d5c9","tid":1658122,"uid":226959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T13:46:38.000Z","msg":"推"}]}